Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがてぇ　スモモか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おう　ふたば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大きくなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お帰り　幹太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:12.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今度はどんな所行ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:14.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,東のでっかい町でな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:18.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ズラリと立派な屋敷の並ぶところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:20.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこで一番の屋敷を建ててきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで竜宮城みたいでな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:30.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子　寂しがってたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう少し　近くで仕事したら？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたの腕なら　どこでだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:44.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺は知らない土地を　腕一本で渡ってくのが面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,世の中にゃ　本当にいろんなところがあるもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:55.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう少し　年を喰ったら落ち着くからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,偉くはっきりとした夢だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まただ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また　あの木の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもあの木　なんだか見覚えがあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:10.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,杉の巨木？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:15.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　幹周りが大人の男で五六人分ありそうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:18.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　そんなのここらじゃ聞かねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:29.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,邪魔するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　どっかで会ったことがあるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:38.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかい　こっちには覚えはねぇが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　間違いねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたは山の中を五六人と連れ立って歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それからまた山ん中を歩いてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたは十ほどの子供だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一行にゃもう一人子供がいたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それから長老の爺さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの爺さんは子供のころからよく見た顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい待て　何で爺さんの子供のころなんて知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　年いくつだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういやそうだな　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:13.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何で俺こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰かに聞いたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　出鱈目言ってんじゃねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何か急に思い出したというか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:31.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,新手のペテンなら　もう少しうまくやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　違うんだよ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里ができてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:06.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この里　どこかで見た
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見覚えがあるわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは　この山から見た俺の里だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木は　この辺りのはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これでようやく謎が解ける
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ…か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さて　帰るか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,抜けねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　誰かいないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,た　助けてくれ　足が…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,遅かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんに会った後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ふと思い当たることがあってな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一人の人が知りえるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ある一定の場所の　遥か昔の出来事を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで　その目で見てきたかのように
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,つぶさに語る者がいる…と
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,な　何でこんなことになった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まるで足が木になっちまったみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ぴくりともしねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,スモモに似た赤い実を先頃食ったはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:29.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつは　「覚木」という蟲でした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木の内部に宿り　養分を得るものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木の本体が危機に陥ると　赤い花のようなものをつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:43.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがてひとつの実に姿を変えて　木から離れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その実には　木の記憶が封じ込められている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:53.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　獣や鳥に食われると
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その体内に巣食い　宿主が木に近づくのを待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,宿主が木に長い間触れていると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木と融合し動けなくさせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて完全に木と同化させてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで　どうすればこの足は治るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,治す術は見つかっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,宿主が危険に曝されれば出ていくんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　死ぬふりをしたらどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:29.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,花をつけることはあっても　実をつけて抜けることはないという
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:36.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,覚木には　本当の危機とそれ以外とを見極める能力があるらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恐らく　それを見極めるために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木の膨大な記憶を利用するのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　何か手はないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな　こんな足じゃ俺はどうやって…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,幹太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私はあんたの命が奪われずに済んで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それだけでありがたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家族みんなで助けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,みんなの世話になって生きてくなんでまっぴらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なぁ　頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:13.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,治してくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,僅かな手がかりでもあればいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの時のあの木　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,切られちまったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この木は千年もここに立ち続けているという
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,イサザ　ちゃんと聞かんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だって俺　この話何度も聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:14.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何度でも聞け　忘れんように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:20.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前もいずれ　若い渡りに言い伝えられるようにな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:27.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この木にはもう長いこと　覚木が住んどる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:34.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつは今までに　二度ほど　赤い花をつけたことがあるという
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:37.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これがその花だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:43.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一度目に咲いたのは　五百五十年ほど昔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この地に大地震のあったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:52.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,地が割れ　根から倒れそうになったが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何とか生き延びたという
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,二度目は　百七十年ほど前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この木に雷が落ちり　傷を負った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:11.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　近くの里の者たちが懸命にその傷を治し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,再びこの木は生き長らえた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:19.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　あそこに見える里だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:25.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの里の者らがここへ来たのは三百年ほど前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:31.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山を開くのにこの木を切ろうとしたが　どうやっても切れなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで人々はこの木を恐れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:41.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて神木と祭り　大事にしたのだという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:44.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここは光脈筋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:50.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,長くそこに生きた木は時に特殊な力を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:53.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の力が及ばんこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:59.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしも子供の頃からいろんな巨木を見てきたが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:03.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これほど大きく見える木はそうはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:10.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　この頃はこの木を訪れる里の者の姿は減った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつが少々気にかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,かつてはご神木だったそうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:38.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ　それは立派な木でしたから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがなぜこんなことに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆　怯えていたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:52.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままではきっと里は終わりだと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは今から15年ほど前　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:03.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,当時　里の大半の者が杣人として木を育て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:06.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,売ることを生業としていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆起きろ　大変じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山が…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体　どうすりゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:27.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう頼る当てもねぇ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里を下りて物乞いをやるしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:38.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,な　あの大杉　町の材木商が大金で買いたいと言ってたろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　あの木は無事だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　あの木は…なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それに絶対切れないって話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなもの　やってみなけりゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おう　やろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　待たんか　お前たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ以上待てねぇ　うちの子はこのままじゃ死んじまう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うちもだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:04.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの木は先祖は代々大事にしてきたご神木だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当に切れなきゃ諦めるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:09.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　あの花は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだか恐ろしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木が怒っているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を言っている　どこに花なんか　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい加減なことを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　止せ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,切れるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　切れないなんて迷信だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:37.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だ　この水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どんどん広がっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:28.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その木は里全体がしばし暮らせる程の額で売れました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:35.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　焼けた山も不思議な速さで蘇っていきました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:41.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,当時　幼かった幹太が無事に育ったのも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この木のおかげなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:48.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああしなければ　今の里はなかったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:55.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　あの時やはりこの木は怒っていたのでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは報いなんでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草木は怒ったりしませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:09.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　何も感じないわけでも　何もしないわけでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ある種の木は害虫が大量に湧くと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その葉から毒を出して自分の身を守る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草木は自ら動けない　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だがその分　周囲の変化を敏感に感じ取り
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,時にそれに応じて自らを変える術を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この木には人の斧を寄せ付けないほどの力があった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがなぜその時は切れたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それはこの木が自ら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その身を切られるよう変化させたせいなのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,傷ついた山全体のために
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,木がそんなことを…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さてね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしそうだとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:08.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私達は本当に大事なものを失くしてしまったんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これを飲んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで足が治るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　蟲の成長を抑えるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,足の治療法は知人にいろいろ文を出してみたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,良い返事のものはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これからも調査を続けてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,別の蟲師に当ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何かあったら　ここに文をくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　お外行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまんな　父ちゃんはもう前のようには…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お話して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:12.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　してやれる話もないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:21.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの木のせいでなぜ俺がこんな目に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とうに切られた木のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なぜいつまでも俺の中に居座り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤い…花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さん　体の具合はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　別に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　何か起こる前兆だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:05.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたの身に危険の及ぶ何か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:23.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だろう　この気配
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,草木が騒いでいる　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この気配は知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:38.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,遥か　遥か昔に一度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:42.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思い出せ　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの時　何が起こったか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,え　何だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今すぐ全員集まれとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何なんだ　一体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく急げって　幹太が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここらでいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　ここらは危ない　まだ先だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,急がねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうじきだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よう　調子はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見ての通りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　この中にいたらと思うとな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,幹太の奴　何で分かったんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:11.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この間15年前に切ったあの大杉に取り憑かれただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:15.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それ以来偉い昔のことまで知ってるんだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:19.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがわしのひい爺さんの話と同じでな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:25.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしらはまたあの大杉に助けられたのかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:31.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すまないな　自分の家も大変だろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:36.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気にするな　命の恩人なんだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうそう　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの大杉を切ってしまったことは今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆古傷のように残ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,受けた恩も　もう返せない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:50.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから　お前に返させてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,困ったことがあったら　里の皆で助ける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:59.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,またあの木が教えてくれることがあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしらにも教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:13.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気の遠くなるような長い長い時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:21.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この地には一本の木が立っていた
